00:08.709 --> 00:11.642
TELL ME.
IT'S A GIRL.

00:11.642 --> 00:15.015
YOU DISAPPEAR TO LOS ANGELES.
YOU DON'T RETURN MY CALLS,

00:15.015 --> 00:17.017
I'M WORRIED ABOUT YOU.
WE ALL ARE.

00:17.017 --> 00:19.019
I KNOW WHEN A MAN IS WILLING

00:19.019 --> 00:21.052
TO SACRIFICE ANYTHING
FOR HIS CAUSE,

00:21.052 --> 00:23.454
AND YOU'RE NOT THAT KIND OF MAN,
AGENT BENFORD.

00:23.454 --> 00:26.057
I NEED A FAVOR--A BIG FAVOR.

00:26.057 --> 00:28.159
IT'S FOR TRACY.

00:28.159 --> 00:30.030
HI, DAD.

00:30.030 --> 00:32.063
WHAT I SAW, WHAT YOU SAW,

00:32.063 --> 00:35.035
