03:01.882 --> 03:04.455
WHAT THIS GUY APPARENTLY
WAS TRYING TO SHOW US

03:04.455 --> 03:07.218
IS WE CAN'T TAKE
WHAT WE SAW FOR GRANTED.

03:07.218 --> 03:09.220
OKAY, BOTTOM LINE IS,
THIS IS A NEW WORLD.

03:09.220 --> 03:12.393
THIS IS A NEW DAY, AND I JUST
THINK WE NEED TO TAKE A MOMENT

03:12.393 --> 03:14.865
AND LET THAT SINK IN.

03:14.865 --> 03:17.398
WHAT WE NEED TO HAVE ANSWERED
RIGHT NOW IS THE QUESTION,

03:17.398 --> 03:20.601
IS THERE GOING TO BE
ANOTHER WORLD BLACKOUT?
MM.

03:20.601 --> 03:23.604
PEOPLE ARE TERRIFIED.
LET'S GET BACK
TO THE BIG QUESTION.

03:23.604 --> 03:25.736
WHAT BIG QUESTION?
DO WE HAVE FREE WILL?

03:25.736 --> 03:28.979
THAT'S THE BIG QUESTION?
POSSIBLY THE CENTRAL QUESTION
OF HUMAN EXISTENCE

03:28.979 --> 03:30.711
FOR MILLENNIA.

03:30.711 --> 03:33.614
(clears throat)

03:35.215 --> 03:37.348
IF THIS IS SUPPOSED
TO BE YOUR RESIGNATION...

03:37.348 --> 03:39.219
(typing on keyboard)
YOU CAN FORGET IT.

03:39.219 --> 03:42.222
YOU'RE NOT EVEN GONNA LET ME
EXPLAIN MYSELF?

03:42.222 --> 03:46.297
YOU WERE ATTACKED.
YOU WERE SHOT.

03:46.297 --> 03:48.259
YOU RETURNED TO DUTY
TO FIND OUT

03:48.259 --> 03:50.331
A COWORKER
JUMPED OFF A BUILDING.

03:50.331 --> 03:53.504
AM I IN
THE RIGHT BALLPARK HERE?

03:53.504 --> 03:57.408
MY LIFE'S NOT MAKING
A WHOLE LOT OF SENSE RIGHT NOW,

03:57.408 --> 04:00.911
AND I THINK I NEED A LITTLE
TIME OFF TO FIGURE IT OUT.

04:00.911 --> 04:02.813
TOTALLY UNDERSTANDABLE.

04:02.813 --> 04:06.317
BUT, UH, I NEED YOU HERE.

04:06.317 --> 04:10.651
I KNOW WE'VE BEEN SHORTHANDED
SINCE THE BLACKOUT.

04:10.651 --> 04:12.523
BUT EVER SINCE GOUGH...

04:13.954 --> 04:16.527
SINCE AL--

04:16.527 --> 04:18.989
THIS ISN'T ABOUT AL.
YES, IT IS.

04:21.332 --> 04:23.434
WHEN I FOUND OUT
ABOUT WHAT HE DID

04:23.434 --> 04:25.265
AND WHY HE DID IT,

04:25.265 --> 04:28.669
IT JUST REALLY MADE ME THINK
ABOUT MY OWN FUTURE.

04:28.669 --> 04:31.772
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I'M SUPPOSED TO DO.

04:31.772 --> 04:34.274
DO I LEAN INTO WHAT I SAW?

04:34.274 --> 04:36.607
DO I FIGHT IT?

04:36.607 --> 04:39.450
WHAT IF
MY GETTING SHOT WAS...

04:39.450 --> 04:41.452
I DON'T EVEN KNOW--

04:41.452 --> 04:45.456
SOME--SOME SORT OF A SIGN THAT
THIS BABY'S NOT MEANT TO BE?

04:45.456 --> 04:47.458
YOU'RE GONNA LET
A BULLET DECIDE

04:47.458 --> 04:50.891
WHETHER OR NOT YOU BRING
A BABY INTO THIS WORLD?

04:52.963 --> 04:55.696
IF AL'S DEATH
PROVED ANYTHING,

04:55.696 --> 04:59.029
IT'S THAT OUR CHOICES
STILL MATTER,

04:59.029 --> 05:01.602
NOW MORE THAN EVER.

05:05.736 --> 05:08.779
WELL, I BELIEVE
WITHOUT RESERVATION

05:08.779 --> 05:10.781
OR RECRIMINATION

05:10.781 --> 05:12.543
THAT YOUR CARD

05:12.543 --> 05:14.885
IS THE ACE OF SPADES.

05:14.885 --> 05:16.717
(laughs)

05:16.717 --> 05:19.820
(Simon) WELL, THAT CERTAINLY
ANSWERS THAT QUESTION.

05:19.820 --> 05:21.822
I'VE BEEN WONDERING
HOW A NOBEL FINALIST

05:21.822 --> 05:24.024
AND RECIPIENT
OF THE MacARTHUR PRIZE

05:24.024 --> 05:27.798
SPENDS HIS IDLE MOMENTS.
THIS ISN'T THE TIME
OR THE PLACE, SIMON.

05:27.798 --> 05:30.030
YOU DROPPED OFF
THE RADAR, LLOYD.

05:30.030 --> 05:32.363
WITHOUT SO MUCH
AS A PHONE CALL.

05:32.363 --> 05:34.365
I'VE HAD TO CHECK MYSELF
INTO THE HOSPITAL

05:34.365 --> 05:36.767
TO HAVE MY BRUISED EGO
X-RAYED.

05:36.767 --> 05:39.009
HELLO, DYLAN.

05:39.009 --> 05:40.941
REMEMBER ME?

05:40.941 --> 05:43.874
(goofy voice) WHY,
THIS IS NOT MY PANCAKE!

05:43.874 --> 05:47.017
WE'RE NOT HAVING THIS
DISCUSSION IN FRONT OF MY SON.
(normal voice)
YEAH, WELL, I'M DONE

05:47.017 --> 05:49.550
HAVING YOU DICTATE
WHEN AND WHERE WE TALK.

05:49.550 --> 05:51.882
MYHILL FORWARDED ME
THE E-MAIL YOU SENT HIM.

05:51.882 --> 05:54.485
OR SHOULD I CALL IT
A SUICIDE NOTE?
IT'S THE ONLY LOGICAL MOVE.

05:54.485 --> 05:56.727
IF YOU'RE HELL-BENT
ON SELF-DESTRUCTION,

05:56.727 --> 05:59.430
THEN, YES, I SUPPOSE IT IS.

05:59.430 --> 06:03.033
BUT I STILL HAVE DOUBTS AS TO
THE CAUSE OF THE BLACKOUT.
OUR EXPERIMENT KILLED
20 MILLION PEOPLE, SIMON.

06:03.033 --> 06:05.135
20 MILLION.

06:05.135 --> 06:07.398
THE WORLD HAS BEEN UPENDED.

06:07.398 --> 06:09.940
PEOPLE NEED ANSWERS.

06:09.940 --> 06:12.643
WE HAVE TO GO PUBLIC
AND TELL THE WORLD

06:12.643 --> 06:15.876
THAT WE CAUSED THE BLACKOUT.

06:17.948 --> 06:19.950
(surf rolling in distance)
ALL RIGHT.

06:19.950 --> 06:23.153
I GUESS WE HAVE TO LEAVE
THIS ROOM SOMETIME.

06:23.153 --> 06:24.955
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

06:24.955 --> 06:28.819
I HAVE A RESERVATION WITH
THE HOTEL THAT SAYS DIFFERENT.

06:28.819 --> 06:29.960
OH.

06:29.960 --> 06:33.023
PLUS YOU HAVEN'T OPENED
YOUR GIFT YET.

06:33.023 --> 06:34.995
MM, WHAT'S THIS?

06:34.995 --> 06:36.667
OH...

06:36.667 --> 06:40.871
JUST A LITTLE SOMETHING
TO CELEBRATE.

06:40.871 --> 06:43.834
AND WHAT ARE WE
CELEBRATING?

06:43.834 --> 06:45.906
SECOND CHANCES, I GUESS...

06:47.578 --> 06:51.041
(lowers voice) AND THE FACT THAT
WE CAN CHANGE THE THINGS WE SAW.

06:51.041 --> 06:56.687
I NEVER THOUGHT WE COULDN'T,
MARK.

06:58.749 --> 07:02.753
(cell phone ringing)

07:02.753 --> 07:03.954
(ring)

07:03.954 --> 07:06.126
THAT'S THE OFFICE.
MM-HMM.

07:06.126 --> 07:09.129
I TOLD 'EM NOT TO CALL
UNLESS IT WAS AN EMERGENCY.
MM-HMM.

07:09.129 --> 07:10.961
I PROMISE.
MM-HMM.

07:10.961 --> 07:13.033
(sighs)

07:13.033 --> 07:15.035
YEAH.
(Demetri) Hey, it's me.

07:15.035 --> 07:18.008
THIS BETTER BE GOOD, DEM.

07:18.008 --> 07:20.541
YEAH, I'M SORRY, MAN.
UM, SOMETHING CAME UP.

07:20.541 --> 07:23.013
Did you bring your laptop?
YEAH.

07:23.013 --> 07:24.975
I'M SENDING YOU SOME VIDEO

07:24.975 --> 07:26.977
WE GOT FROM BARSTOW P.D.
THIS MORNING.

07:26.977 --> 07:29.520
Remember when you had Marcie
plug all the clues

07:29.520 --> 07:33.153
off the Mosaic board
into NCIC?
YOU'VE GOT SOMETHING?

07:33.153 --> 07:35.556
Yeah. Barstow P.D.
caught a homicide.

07:35.556 --> 07:38.188
Eyewitness managed to
record it on her cell phone.

07:38.188 --> 07:42.132
When it hit the system,
NCIC kicked back a red flag.
WHY?

07:42.132 --> 07:43.994
Stay tuned, man.

07:43.994 --> 07:45.766
(gunshot)

07:50.170 --> 07:52.503
(whoosh)

07:53.904 --> 07:56.807
I'M HEADED BACK RIGHT NOW.

08:06.056 --> 08:10.991
