08:17.998 --> 08:20.230
WHAT DO WE HAVE?

08:20.230 --> 08:22.833
ANYTHING THAT MIGHT HELP US
I.D. OUR TATTOOED FRIEND?
NOT REALLY.

08:22.833 --> 08:24.975
THE VICTIM, NEIL PAROFSKY,
IS AN AERONAUTICS ENGINEER

08:24.975 --> 08:27.037
WHO WORKS OUT OF A PLANT
IN EL SEGUNDO.

08:27.037 --> 08:29.940
WATCH AND WALLET WERE MISSING,
SO EVERYBODY'S THINKING ROBBERY.

08:29.940 --> 08:33.513
IS THAT CONFIRMED BY WHOEVER
SHOT THE CELL PHONE VIDEO?
UH, INGRID ALVAREZ.

08:33.513 --> 08:35.786
YEAH, SHE SAW PAROFSKY
HAND SOMETHING OVER

08:35.786 --> 08:38.819
BEFORE HE GOT SHOT, SO SHE
THOUGHT IT WAS A MUGGING, TOO.

08:38.819 --> 08:39.920
GREAT.

08:39.920 --> 08:41.922
FIRST DAY BACK?

08:41.922 --> 08:44.895
I SHOULD HAVE
GOTTEN YOU FLOWERS.

